MODLIST [match string]

List the modules that are currently loaded into the
ircd, along with their address and version.
When a match string is provided, modlist only prints
modules with names matching the match string.

- Requires Oper Priv: A

MODLIST match_string irc.server

List the modules currently loaded into the remote
server, along with address and version, if the server
accepts remote module loading.

NOTE: A match string must be provided.  Use * to list
all modules on the other server.

- Requires Oper Priv: A
